.pg
.\"O Doorways connect rooms and corridors.  Some doorways have no doors;
.\"O you can walk right through.  Others have doors in them, which may be
.\"O open, closed, or locked.  To open a closed door, use the `o' (open)
.\"O command; to close it again, use the `c' (close) command.
